CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 5, 1946, pg. 13, reads: "Riding High! Gayle Gordon, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Leonard S. Gordon, Washington, D. C., rides her new hobby horse with caution.  Her family spent the holidays here with her grandparents."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Gayle Gordon riding rocking horse on table, in domestic interior with Christmas tree in background, vertical format
